後大戰全員出嚟嗰幕加好多分<br />\n即刻諗起魔戒召到死靈軍團嗰幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋結局美隊都過急 搞到第一感覺係做乜鳩<br />\n可能得三個鐘搞到個節奏怪怪地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:16:56.000Z","msg":"仲有hulk真係好失敗<br />\n智慧融合完 成套戲淨係負責撳掣 啪手指同掟櫈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8fa94e33cb92b78619f5445c40c274fea680f6","tid":1140110,"uid":138613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a541ccec0c632eeec915eec970bc25dc01b507eb","tid":1140110,"uid":158755,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n今日無咁多配合角色特性嘅打鬥<br />\n變左每人都走去單挑Thanos，例如wanda,thor,im,ca,cm等等全部單挑多<br />\nWanda控緊thanos嗰時又唔炸佢又唔電佢個個食花生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:19:13.000Z","msg":"thor 同sw應該係第一次見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n不過你啱，真係電下佢都好<br />\n咁好機會定住咗都冇追擊"},{"pid":"c65bfc3b95c596df091bc2c5a816c22665e17274","tid":1140110,"uid":61994,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:23:02.000Z","msg":"(個人睇到鷹眼同日本佬講野真係覺得好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n呢個真係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,鷹眼想玩刀姐唔駛特登整呢段出黎<br />\n反而搞到佢無哂個人特色"},{"pid":"ce18f1598aeac4c290af232195afe1c8b93b96a2","tid":1140110,"uid":24045,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:26:04.000Z","msg":"真,唔值咁高分同票房,只係fans對avengers既支持"},{"pid":"925c0fe85f94d256c848a7cd5e148dcb72da8c7b","tid":1140110,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46a3a976c65836cc2921bbb43aeecc98c504e54b","tid":1140110,"uid":45829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"endgame啲打鬥真係唔合乎預期地令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054633528d1c3ebe291bf4677a51ae35d96dd6ba","tid":1140110,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef8fa94e33cb92b78619f5445c40c274fea680f6","tid":1140110,"uid":138613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a541ccec0c632eeec915eec970bc25dc01b507eb","tid":1140110,"uid":158755,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n今日無咁多配合角色特性嘅打鬥<br />\n變左每人都走去單挑Thanos，例如wanda,thor,im,ca,cm等等全部單挑多<br />\nWanda控緊thanos嗰時又唔炸佢又唔電佢個個食花生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:19:13.000Z","msg":"thor 同sw應該係第一次見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n不過你啱，真係電下佢都好<br />\n咁好機會定住咗都冇追擊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T00:28:04.000Z","msg":"唔記得了，打奧創無見過？"},{"pid":"28186bf1100aebe5da44441bce85e9971713f774","tid":1140110,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T00:39:33.000Z","msg":"樓主RIP"},{"pid":"ba577f726e5bf82580f5faa8c97db1ad9878f550","tid":1140110,"uid":18107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T00:46:12.000Z","msg":"上集變粉果d都係為出黎而出黎,唯一有印象d係得蜘蛛仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52b67eb348b661a6ba26ce017c926e34d914ad7","tid":1140110,"uid":114275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T01:39:13.000Z","msg":"我自己嘅睇法啦<br />\n<br />\n其實最後一集 嗰氣氛 節奏 表達嘅變調應該先係神粹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一嚟 第三集其實係講一班 superhero 最後都失敗咗<br />\n<br />\n而第四集照返個 flow 係應該大家強調失敗後要付出代價<br />\n<br />\n而唔係好似一般英雄片咁最後勝利 happy ending<br />\n<br />\n勾劃返呢一個情緒其實應該係重點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二嚟 舖路俾幾個主要角色嘅引退 / 離開 <br />\n<br />\n用章節去填補返佢地嘅遺憾係一個好好嘅做法 <br />\n<br />\n完滿咗佢地嘅告別<br />\n<br />\n當然打交都係重要同吸引嘅<br />\n<br />\n但係 d 場景應該要體現多 d 各英雄喺上次失敗之後嘅得着<br />\n<br />\n而唔係又玩大堆頭鳩打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係我都同意套戲喺表達呢 d 轉折唔係做得好理想</span><br />\n<br />\n感情位同視覺刺激都唔係好出色 無論係音樂 對白 動作場面等<br />\n<br />\n到喉唔到肺 兩種氣氛都唔係太出到 <br />\n<br />\n好似搖擺不定 驚是但一邊太重觀眾要接唔到咁<br />\n<br />\n可以做得更好"},{"pid":"6f321571adec4cba2eecbaf348895f80d163d39b","tid":1140110,"uid":171310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T01:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}